ate:** On session TurnStart, if on a non-main branch without a trail, one is auto-created with `in_progress` status. Skipped when trails are disabled.\\n\\n**Push:** Pre-push hooks push `entire/trails` branch alongside `entire/checkpoints/v1`. Skipped when trails are disabled.\\n\\n**Settings key:** `strategy_options.trails` — `true` (default/missing) = enabled, `false` = disabled.\\n\\n**Storage:** `entire/trails` orphan branch with sharded paths: `<trail_id[:2]>/<trail_id[2:]>/metadata.json`\\n\\n**Status lifecycle:** `draft → open → in_progress → in_review → done → closed`\\n\\n#### Session Package (`cmd/entire/cli/session/`)\\n- `session.go` - Session data types and interfaces\\n- `state.go` - `StateStore` for managing `.git/entire-sessions/` files\\n- `phase.go` - Session phase state machine (phases, events, transitions, actions)\\n\\n#### Session Phase State Machine\\n\\nSessions track their lifecycle through phases managed by a state machine in `session/phase.go`:\\n\\n**Phases:** `ACTIVE`, `IDLE`, `ENDED`\\n\",\"numLines\":40,\"startLine\":340,\"totalLines\":623}},\"sourceToolAssistantUUID\":\"f35b3222-0cfa-4cf4-bdd7-8e37f955a068\"}\n{\"type\":\"file-history-snapshot\",\"messageId\":\"1e0b802b-eb08-4994-8a4a-252eb6beb22c\",\"snapshot\":{\"messageId\":\"e01109d1-65c8-40c6-9cc3-410b4708be0e\",\"trackedFileBackups\":{\"cmd/entire/cli/trail/trail.go\":{\"backupFileName\":\"9707c8f151e6b99e@v1\",\"version\":1,\"backupTime\":\"2026-02-20T17:54:35.916Z\"},\"cmd/entire/cli/trail/store.go\":{\"backupFileName\":\"9fb57b7a53395cca@v1\",\"version\":1,\"backupTime\":\"2026-02-20T17:54:44.658Z\"},\"cmd/entire/cli/trail_cmd.go\":{\"backupFileName\":\"4403a6c6f71d4713@v1\",\"version\":1,\"backupTime\":\"2026-02-20T17:55:42.950Z\"},\"cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_types.go\":{\"backupFileName\":\"117822660e79db9c@v1\",\"version\":1,\"backupTime\":\"2026-02-20T17:56:00.408Z\"},\"cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_condensation.go\":{\"backupFileName\":\"b50416eb05776